==Charts and Chart Performance==
"Mercy" was an European top 5 hit, reaching number 1 in [[Austria]], [[Germany]], [[Greece]], [[Ireland]], [[Netherlands]], [[Norway]], [[Spain]], [[Switzerland]], and the [[UK]], not to mention topping the [[Eurochart Hot 100]] three times, once in March, once in April and once in June. Although internationally the song wasn't as well received, it still managed to reach the top 5 in some countries, including [[Japan]], [[New Zealand]], [[Turkey]] and [[Venezuela]], while reaching the top 20 in [[Canada]] and the top 40 in [[Australia]] and [[U.S.A.]].

Mercy spend most of 2008 in the Australian iTunes top 100. As of February 24, 2009 it had reached it's all time peak of 18, 51 weeks after release.

